reviewText: Great and Enjoyable...must watch for all aviation enthusiasts!
One of the best airport programs that I've purchased.

JustPlanes.com has produced an excellent video.  The footage of aircraft arrivals, departures, and ground movements at LAX is incredible.  This is a professionally done video, and the production company obviously had excellent access to the airport.  Lots of great commercial aircraft, including some interesting surprises.  This video is a must for any aviation enthusiast!
